org.sxb.data.redis.support.atomic

クラス RedisAtomicDouble

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Number
      • org.sxb.data.redis.support.atomic.RedisAtomicDouble
  • すべての実装されたインタフェース:
    java.io.Serializable, BoundKeyOperations<java.lang.String>

    public class RedisAtomicDouble
extends java.lang.Number
implements java.io.Serializable, BoundKeyOperations<java.lang.String>
    Atomic double backed by Redis. Uses Redis atomic increment/decrement and watch/multi/exec operations for CAS operations.
    作成者:
    Jennifer Hickey, Thomas Darimont
    関連項目:
    直列化された形式

      • RedisAtomicDouble

        public RedisAtomicDouble(java.lang.String redisCounter,
                         RedisOperations<java.lang.String,java.lang.Double> template,
                         double initialValue)
        Constructs a new RedisAtomicDouble instance. Note: You need to configure the given template with appropriate RedisSerializer for the key and value. As an alternative one could use the RedisAtomicDouble(String, RedisConnectionFactory, Double) constructor which uses appropriate default serializers.
        パラメータ:
        redisCounter - the redis counter
        template - the template
        initialValue - the initial value

        public boolean compareAndSet(double expect,
                             double update)

        パラメータ:
        expect - the expected value
        update - the new value
        戻り値:
        true if successful. False return indicates that the actual value was not equal to the expected value.
